director.name: 奥斯汀·林奇 Austin Jack Lynch

introduction: What is the Interview Project?David Lynch describes it as "a 20,000-mile road trip over 70 days across and back the United States" where "people have been found and interviewed," and if you watch the videos this trip produced, you're "going to meet hundreds of people," all different, found "by driving along the roads, going into bars, going into different locations, and there they were.Official Website:http://interviewproject.davidlynch.com/
